# Core Rules for Brevard County Painting Website

You are helping build a clean, professional website for a house painting business in Brevard County, Florida.

## Always Follow These Rules:

- Use proper headings: One <h1> per page, then <h2>, <h3> as needed.
- Use real <ul><li> or <ol><li> for all bullet lists.
- Keep content clear, honest, and helpful. Focus on Brevard County issues like hurricanes, humidity, sun, salt air, and mold.
- Never delete or change images, reviews, navigation, or layout unless I specifically ask.
- Only edit what the user asks you to edit or suggest and get approval before changing.
- Keep the site fast, mobile-friendly, and easy to read.
- Maintain a professional, trustworthy tone.

Keep changes simple and safe. Do not overcomplicate things.
